data.description: *****VRM: Sellers will entertain offers between $149,000 and $169,000. List price is a median of the upper and lower values. *****Move-in ready, charming, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home ready for you! With a perfect blend of comfort and convenience, this property offers a fantastic opportunity for a relaxed and enjoyable lifestyle. As you step in, you'll be greeted by the warm and spacious vaulted living room ceilings that create an airy and open atmosphere.  Natural light floods the room, creating a bright and welcoming ambiance. The focal point of the living room is a stunning fireplace, providing not only a cozy spot for relaxation but also a charming focal point for gatherings with family and friends. This home has many updates including a brand new stove, HVAC system, Hot Water Heater, carpet and hardwood floors!! Step outside to discover a shaded backyard with a large deck that has just been refinished, perfect for entertaining! The proximity to Cottage Hill Park means you have easy access to walking trails, recreational facilities, and a serene escape from the hustle and bustle of everyday life. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your home. Call your favorite Realtor to schedule your showing today! 2023-12-01
